  "synopsis": "When a little traveler chick was singing and traveling happily in the spring forest, he heard the cry of an umbrella. It turned out that the owner of the umbrella had lost it. After the chick comforted it, the two friends went on the road together. \n\nAlong the way, their team gradually added a wheel that fell into pits and a ball that got stuck between branches. Because they helped each other, the four friends’ journey was filled with laughter and singing.\n\n(Source: Baidu, translated)",
